Package org.databene.domain.organization

Class Summary
CompanyName Assembles the parts of a company name, providing access to full name, short name and name parts like core name (which is the shortName), sector, location and legal form.
CompanyNameGenerator Generates company names.
DepartmentNameGenerator Creates random department names based on a Locale-specific CSV file.
LegalFormGenerator Generates the abbreviated strings for legal forms of organizations.
SectorGenerator Generator implementation which creates names of industry sectors.
